OL,3,CGovernment say agreement on
OL,4,CHillsborough Law could come in weeks
OL,6,FThe topic was brought up in the House
OL,7,Fof Lords
OL,9,FThe Government is "hopeful" it can
OL,10,Fcome to an agreement on a Hillsborough
OL,11,FLaw with the families impacted by the
OL,12,Fdisaster "in the coming weeks and
OL,13,Fmonths", the House of Lords has heard.
OL,15,FSpeaking from the Government front
OL,16,Fbench, Lord Ponsonby of Shulbrede said
OL,17,Ftalks "have been going positively", as
OL,18,Fpeers raised concerns the duty of
OL,19,Fcandour element of the proposed law is
OL,20,Fbeing watered down.
