OL,6,FLabour peer Baroness Chakrabarti said
OL,7,Fthe families of the 97 football fans
OL,8,Fwho died following the 1989 incident
OL,9,Ffeel "less positive" about its
OL,10,Fdiscussions with the Government.
OL,12,FThe deadly crush occurred during the
OL,13,FFA Cup semi-final between Liverpool
OL,14,Fand Nottingham Forest at the football
OL,15,Fground in Sheffield.
