OL,3,CGovernment say agreement on
OL,4,CHillsborough Law could come in weeks
OL,6,FThe proposed law would require public
OL,7,Fbodies to have a duty of candour,
OL,8,Fmeaning they would need to co-operate
OL,9,Fwith official inquiries and tell the
OL,10,Ftruth in the aftermath of major
OL,11,Fdisasters ` or face criminal sanctions.
OL,13,FA previous deadline set by Labour,
OL,14,Fthat the Bill would be passed before
OL,15,Fthe anniversary of the Hillsborough
OL,16,Fdisaster in April, has been missed.
OL,18,FThe Government had said it needed more
OL,19,Ftime to finalise the Bill.
