OL,6,FA draft Bill has been criticised by
OL,7,Fcampaigners, including the
OL,8,FHillsborough Law Now group, for not
OL,9,Fcontaining pledges previously made `
OL,10,Fincluding the duty of candour.
OL,12,FLady Chakrabarti told the upper
OL,13,Fchamber on Thursday: "I'm grateful to
OL,14,F(the minister), as always, for
OL,15,Frepeating the Government's commitment
OL,16,Fto introduce Hillsborough Law, but I'm
OL,17,Fafraid that the families and their
OL,18,Frepresentatives feel a little less
OL,19,Fpositive about the engagement they had
OL,20,Fso far.
OL,26,@uD@VOU
