OL,6,FHe had earlier said: "Since March, we
OL,7,Fhave listened to stakeholder feedback
OL,8,Fto ensure that we deliver the best
OL,9,FBill possible.
OL,11,F"This engagement has been constructive
OL,12,Fand progress has been made. Engagement
OL,13,Fis ongoing and will continue over the
OL,14,Fsummer."
OL,16,FLiberal Democrat peer Lord Storey
OL,17,Fsaid: "Would he give a clear
OL,18,Fcommitment there will be no watering
OL,19,Fdown of that duty of candour intent
OL,20,Fwhen the Bill is published?"
