OL,6,FLord Ponsonby replied: "The Prime
OL,7,FMinister has made a personal
OL,8,Fcommitment to the affected families to
OL,9,Fwork with them constructively to come
OL,10,Fup with an appropriate law.
OL,12,F"Regarding the duty of candour, the
OL,13,FGovernment is clear that what happened
OL,14,Ffollowing the Hillsborough disaster
OL,15,Fmust never happen again.
OL,17,F"Under the Hillsborough Law, public
OL,18,Fofficials will be bound by duties of
OL,19,Fcandour with criminal and professional
OL,20,Fconsequences.
